 Shehu Sani has some suggestions for Nigerians who want to study abroad in the midst of Russia’s invasion of Ukraine. He advised them to return home and enroll at any of Nigeria’s universities. He believes it is preferable to hustle with ASUU than to be stuck in a foreign country by conflict and racism. READ ALSO: How AU Can End Coup In Africa – Shehu Sani This morning, he posted it to his Twitter account. ”Those who are dying to study abroad;Stay at home and get into federal or state university;it’s better to hustle with ASUU than war and racism.” he tweeted See Twitter Post Below: 